snippet.title: DAVE THE DIVER - Official Early Access Annoucement Trailer | gamescom2022
snippet.description:
DAVE THE DIVER features online at gamescom 2022!
and DEMO IS NOW AVAILABLE! Play the DEMO now on Steam.

DAVE THE DIVER  is coming to Steam via Early Access this October.

✨ Add to Steam Wishlist to receive official release notifications!
Community channels are also open to inform game news and communicate with divers, so please we look forward to your interest and participation!

🤿 |  Game Introduction |
Welcome to 'DAVE THE DIVER', a marine adventure set in the mysterious Blue Hole. Explore the sea with Dave by day, and run a sushi restaurant at night. Uncover the secrets of the Blue Hole, and unwrap this deep sea mystery involving 3 friends, each with distinct personalities. New adventures await.

🐬Check out more details on DAVE THE DIVER Steam Page and official community channel!
■ STEAM : [https://nexon.link/8HP] 
■ Discord: [https://discord.gg/davethediver] 
■ Twitter: [https://twitter.com/DaveDiverGame]
■ Website: [https://mintrocketgames.com/en/DaveTheDiver]
